@page "/biografy"

<PageTitle>Biografy - Oceanside Dental Centre</PageTitle>

<!-- Page Header -->
<div class="row bg-ocean-gradient text-white py-3 mb-5">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="col-12 text-center">
            <h1 class="h3 m-0">Biografy</h1>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="container mb-5">
    <div class="row align-items-start">
        <!-- Photo Column -->
        <div class="col-md-4 mb-4 mb-md-0">
            <div class="card border-0 shadow-sm h-100">
                <!-- Doctor's Photo -->
                <img src="images/dr-muzina.jpg" 
                     alt="Dr. Blerina Muzina" 
                     class="card-img-top img-fluid" 
                     style="object-fit: cover; height: 400px;" />
                
                <div class="card-body text-center bg-ocean-gradient text-white">
                    <h5 class="card-title mb-0">Dr. Blerina Muzina</h5>
                    <p class="card-text small">DMD</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Biography Column -->
        <div class="col-md-8">
            <h2 class="h3 text-sage mb-4">Dr. Blerina Muzina, DMD</h2>
            
            <p class="text-justify mb-3">
                Dr. Blerina Muzina earned her Bachelor of Science in Biochemistry from the University of Windsor in 2009. She went on to pursue her passion for dentistry at the University of Saskatchewan, where she received her Doctor of Dental Medicine (DMD) degree in 2014. Following graduation, Dr. Muzina practiced general dentistry for over three years in a close-knit community in rural Saskatchewan, gaining valuable experience in comprehensive patient care.
            </p>

            <p class="text-justify mb-3">
                Seeking the natural beauty and welcoming lifestyle of Vancouver Island, Dr. Muzina and her family relocated to the region. In October 2017, she joined the Oceanside Dental team in Parksville, where she has been providing exceptional family dental care ever since. Known for her gentle approach and dedication to patient comfort, Dr. Muzina is committed to delivering the highest quality care in a friendly and relaxed environment. While she enjoys all aspects of general dentistry, she has a particular passion for restorative and cosmetic dentistry. To ensure her patients benefit from the latest advancements in dental care, she actively pursues continuing education and stays current with evolving technologies.
            </p>

            <p class="text-justify">
                Outside of her professional life, Dr. Muzina cherishes time with her family and friends. She enjoys traveling, hiking, movie nights, and playing with her daughter, embracing every opportunity to create meaningful memories.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
